column5: Most of my family doesnt like talking about my feelings with me, my school counselor said she doesnt care if i commit suicide, and she put hand sanitizer all over my self harm cuts when they were open. I have noone to talk to :(
We could talk if youd like,, im not the best at conversations though
No not really, my most recent therapist kinda does
Thing is ive talked to my family, ive been to five different therapists, ive called hotlines many times and ive gone to a mental hospital.
Yyeah,, also i think it might be one of my medications

I talk to a social worker sometimes but its for gender dysphoria ack,, last time i talked to them i was clean of cutting myself for almost a year and i feel scared to tell them i started again. I dont think any of my teachers genuinely care about me. One of my teachers (my english teacher) always yells at us to be quite and it makes me go into a panic everytime. I dont trust any of the students either, one time after a STAAR test (its the end of the year test here in texas) i was really nervous so i started scratching my arm pretty badly and other kids around me were doing the same thing to mock me. They were staring at me quitely laughing. It made me feel awful. Most of my teachers are loud and very energized which also kinda makes me nervous,,

I dont really trust school counselors anymore. The last one i went to said that she didnt care if i killed myself and that i have to stop going to her office, she also slathered hand santizer on my arm full of open self harm cuts before so hngnhng h
I feel depressed and my head feels really foggy and light headed

I guess so,, i just dont think im patient enough to reach 18. I hate my family, and i hate where i live. My sister always screams at me, punches me, hits me, and scratches me with her nails, and when i piss her off she drags me to my room by the ankles. My grandad things im suicidal just to play with him or to just “torture” his emotions. My brother eats everything so most of the time i dont eat for days at end, im only able to eat lunch at school. I wasnt even consensual either, my dad forced himself onto my mom to have me. 

I dont even have my mom anymore, she passed away. She never really liked me because i guess i was too much of a problem and she always liked my brother more.
I feel like im between life and death constantly, like im only here to count days, doing the same things over and over until i eventually get so tired off it that i end it
Its not really the taste, just a way to feed it to them without having to pick them up
I dont own anything that i could mix it with :”) ill try to give them to it by spoon, but theyll try to fight over it.
I mean she did say shes been wanting to put what happened out there but was too scared to, shes probably relieved that she didn’t receive backlash
Thats a really good idea!! Problem is we dont have either of those things near me :‘)
Idk if the circus is in town :(((
I would, but im not scummy
